## 1. User Onboarding & Authentication — 75% ✅

### ✅ Completed
| Sub-feature | Evidence |
|---|---|
| Registration via Clerk (email + OAuth) | [sign-in page](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/app/(public)/sign-in/[[...sign-in]]/page.tsx), [sign-up page](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/app/(public)/sign-up/[[...sign-up]]/page.tsx) |
| User sync to Supabase on sign-in | [UserSync.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/auth/UserSync.tsx) — calls `/api/create-user` on login |
| Role management (USER, ADMIN, SUPER_ADMIN) | [middleware.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/middleware.ts) — fetches role from `users_profile` table |
| JWT session management via Clerk | Clerk handles sessions; middleware validates with `clerkMiddleware()` |
| Role-based redirection post-login | Middleware redirects USER→`/dashboard`, ADMIN/SUPER_ADMIN→`/admin` |
| Role-based API protection | Middleware blocks non-GET admin API calls for USERs |
| Profile form with Zod validation | [ProfileForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/profile/ProfileForm.tsx), [zod.userProfile.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/services/validations/schemas/zod.userProfile.ts) |
| Profile photo upload | [ProfilePhotoUploader.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/profile/ProfilePhotoUploader.tsx) |
| Profile completion tracking | [profileCompetion.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/services/helper/profileCompetion.ts), [ProfileCompletionCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/user-panel/ProfileCompletionCard.tsx) |
| Role guard hook | [useRoleGuard.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/utils/useRoleGuard.ts), [adminGuard.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/lib/adminGuard.ts) |

### ❌ Not Yet Implemented
| Sub-feature | Notes |
|---|---|
| Phone number registration | Clerk supports it but not configured |
| Identity verification flow | No KYC or document verification implemented |
| Emergency contact at registration | Contacts are added separately, not during registration |

