## 3. Live Location Sharing — 85% ✅

### ✅ Completed
| Sub-feature | Evidence |
|---|---|
| GPS position tracking via `watchPosition` | [useLocationSharing.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/utils/useLocationSharing.ts) |
| Location upsert to Supabase `live_locations` | Same hook — upserts lat/lng/accuracy with interval |
| Real-time map with React Leaflet | [LiveMap.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/user-panel/LiveMap.tsx) — 670 lines |
| Supabase Realtime subscription for circle | [useLiveLocationSubscription.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/utils/useLiveLocationSubscription.ts) — `postgres_changes` |
| Live markers on map for circle members | [LiveMarkersLayer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/user-panel/LiveMarkersLayer.tsx) |
| Toggle start/stop sharing | [SafetyActionBar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/components/user-panel/SafetyActionBar.tsx) — sharing toggle button |
| SOS trigger button | SafetyActionBar — SOS button with pulse animation |
| Time-limited session (1 hour expiry) | [startSharingSession](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/redux/redux-slices/userSafetySlice.ts#76-84) sets `expiresAt` to +1 hour |
| Location history/trail (50 points) | [userSafetySlice.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/redux/redux-slices/userSafetySlice.ts) — `locationHistory` array |
| Adaptive update interval (4s SOS / 10s normal) | [useLocationSharing](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/utils/useLocationSharing.ts#7-134) — checks `safetyStatus === "sos"` |
| Final "OFF" update when sharing stops | [sendFinalUpdate()](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/utils/useLocationSharing.ts#112-130) in useLocationSharing |
| User self-marker on map | `currentCoords` from Redux shown as marker in LiveMap |
| Redux state management for safety | Full `userSafetySlice` with sharing, SOS, geofencing states |

### ❌ Not Yet Implemented
| Sub-feature | Notes |
|---|---|
| Auto-expiry enforcement (timer to stop sharing) | `expiresAt` is stored but no timer auto-stops sharing |
| Map marker smooth movement/animation | Marker updates positions but no smooth interpolation |
| Location log persistence to DB | History only in Redux (client-side), not persisted |

