## 8. Notifications & Alerts — 45% 🔴

### ✅ Completed
| Sub-feature | Evidence |
|---|---|
| Zone entry/exit detection (geofencing engine) | [zoneDetectionEngine.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/utils/zoneDetectionEngine.ts) — ENTER/EXIT/INSIDE events |
| Smart geofencing toggle | SafetyActionBar — [toggleSmartGeofencing](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/hooks/redux/redux-slices/userSafetySlice.ts#130-133) action |
| Safety alert email via Brevo (template-based) | [brevo.api.ts](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/services/api/brevo.api.ts) — sends email with zone name, location link |
| Notify circle on danger toggle | `notify_on_denger` flag per emergency contact |
| Safety logs API | [/api/admin/safety-logs](file:///c:/Users/suman/Desktop/prohorini_0.0.1/src/app/api/admin/safety-logs) — stores zone_alert, sos events |
| In-app toast notifications | Sonner toasts throughout the app |
| Unsafe zone visual alert (HUD) | NearestSafetyHUD shows red banner when inside threat zone |

### ❌ Not Yet Implemented
| Sub-feature | Notes |
|---|---|
| Real-time push notifications (FCM/Web Push) | No service worker or push notification setup |
| Automated geofencing alert pipeline | Zone detection exists but not wired to trigger alerts automatically |
| Alert circle members when sharing toggled | No notification sent when location sharing starts/stops |
| Admin broadcast warnings | No mechanism for admins to send platform-wide alerts |
| SOS notification to circle members | SOS flag updates DB but no email/push sent to contacts |
| Notification inbox/center for users | No in-app notification feed or history |

