## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend
        A[Next.js 16 App] --> B[Clerk Auth]
        A --> C[React Leaflet Maps]
        A --> D[Redux Toolkit State]
        A --> E[React Query Data]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend
        F[Next.js API Routes]
        G[Supabase Realtime]
        H[Brevo Email API]
    end
    
    subgraph Database
        I[(Supabase PostgreSQL)]
    end
    
    A --> F
    A --> G
    F --> I
    F --> H
    G --> I
    
    style A fill:#1e293b,color:#fff
    style I fill:#3ecf8e,color:#fff
    style B fill:#6c47ff,color:#fff
```

---

## 🎯 Priority Recommendations

> [!IMPORTANT]
> ### Top 5 Items to Complete Next
> 1. **SOS notification pipeline** — Wire SOS trigger to send emails/push to emergency contacts
> 2. **Automated geofencing alerts** — Connect zone detection engine → alert dispatcher
> 3. **Anonymous reporting** — Add toggle in crime report modal
> 4. **Sharing auto-expiry timer** — Enforce the `expiresAt` with a countdown + auto-stop
> 5. **Dashboard charts** — Add Recharts/Victory for visual insights on admin dashboard

> [!WARNING]
> ### Security & Production Readiness
> - Rate-limiting is not implemented on crime report API
> - No spam prevention on any endpoint
> - Admin credentials are hardcoded in sign-in page comments — **remove before production**
> - `console.log` statements throughout codebase need cleanup

